http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Visakhapatnam/Spot-painting-contest-on-Jan.-23/article14011690.ece

To build awareness on cleaner fuels among the younger generation, the Ministry of Petroleum and Natural Gas along with Public Sector Oil and Gas companies are celebrating the Oil Conservation Fortnight till January 31.In line with this, Hindustan Petroleum Corporation Limited and Petroleum Conservation and Research Association are organising a spot painting contest with the theme ‘Towards Cleaner Fuels…Greener Planet’ at Gayatri Vidya Parishad MLBT School on January 23.Further details can be had over contact nos: 7836857368 or 9848195946.